---
layout: base.njk
title: Jay Egger — SEO & Growth Strategist
description: SEO and growth strategist who scales traffic, leads, and revenue for content-heavy and finance brands.
permalink: /
---
<header>
    <div class="marquee" aria-hidden="true"><span>Under construction • </span></div>
    <div class="hero" id="top">
      <div class="card hero-copy">
        <h1>Jay Egger</h1>
        <p class="meta">SEO & growth strategist for content-heavy and finance brands.</p>
        <div class="btn-row">
          <a class="btn" href="{{ '/contact/' | url }}">Contact</a>
          <a class="btn secondary" href="{{ '/blog/' | url }}">Blog</a>
        </div>
        <div class="meta">Current: Senior SEO Manager @ SBG Funding — 300% organic growth, 250+ apps/month, ~$125K/mo attributed revenue.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card hero-img">
        <div class="frame">
          <picture>
            <source type="image/webp" srcset="{{ '/assets/jay-egger-headshot-800.webp' | url }}">
            <img src="{{ '/assets/jay-egger-headshot-800.jpg' | url }}" alt="Jay Egger headshot" width="800" height="1000" loading="eager" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high">
          </picture>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="card" id="now">
      <div class="accent">Now</div>
      <p>Running SEO, CRO, and GEO strategy for commercial finance audiences. I build landing pages, content systems, and Python/SQL tools that turn traffic into attributable revenue. Previously scaled WordPress portfolios to 103M monthly sessions, launched House Digest from zero, and shipped AI/E-E-A-T programs across 21 sites.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="card" id="writing">
      <div class="accent">Featured Writing</div>
      {% set featuredPosts = collections.posts | featuredOnly %}
      {% set displayPosts = featuredPosts %}
      {% if not displayPosts or (displayPosts | length) == 0 %}
        {% set displayPosts = collections.posts | slice(0,3) %}
      {% endif %}
      {% if displayPosts and (displayPosts | length) > 0 %}
      <div class="grid-2">
        {% for post in displayPosts %}
          <article>
            <div class="meta">{{ post.date | readableDate }}{% if post.data.tags and (post.data.tags | length) > 0 %} · {{ post.data.tags | join(', ') }}{% endif %}</div>
            <h3><a href="{{ post.url | url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
            <p>{{ post.data.excerpt or post.data.description }}</p>
          </article>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% else %}
      <p class="meta">No posts yet—publish and mark a post as featured to show it here.</p>
      {% endif %}
    </section>

    <section class="card" id="projects">
      <div class="accent">Featured Projects</div>
      {% set featuredProjects = collections.projects | featuredOnly %}
      {% if featuredProjects and (featuredProjects | length) > 0 %}
      <div class="grid-2">
        {% for project in featuredProjects %}
          <article>
            <div class="meta">{% if project.data.status %}{{ project.data.status }}{% endif %}{% if project.data.tech and (project.data.tech | length) > 0 %}{% if project.data.status %} · {% endif %}{{ project.data.tech | join(', ') }}{% endif %}</div>
            <h3><a href="{{ project.url | url }}">{{ project.data.title }}</a></h3>
            <p>{{ project.data.excerpt or project.data.description }}</p>
          </article>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% else %}
      <p class="meta">No featured projects yet.</p>
      {% endif %}
      <div class="btn-row">
        <a class="btn secondary" href="{{ '/projects/' | url }}">View all projects</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="card" id="blog">
      <div class="accent">Blog Roll</div>
      <div class="grid-2">
        {% for post in collections.posts | slice(0,4) %}
          <article>
            <div class="meta">{{ post.date | readableDate }}{% if post.data.tags and (post.data.tags | length) > 0 %} · {{ post.data.tags | join(', ') }}{% endif %}</div>
            <h3><a href="{{ post.url | url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
            <p>{{ post.data.excerpt or post.data.description }}</p>
          </article>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <a class="btn secondary" href="{{ '/blog/' | url }}">View all posts</a>
        <a class="btn secondary" href="{{ '/rss.xml' | url }}">RSS</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="card" id="contact">
      <div class="accent">Contact</div>
      <p>Want to collaborate or hire? Head to the contact page.</p>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <a class="btn" href="{{ '/contact/' | url }}">Open contact form</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="card" id="links">
      <div class="accent">Links</div>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <a class="btn secondary" href="{{ '/assets/jay-egger-resume.pdf' | url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Resume (PDF)</a>
        <a class="btn secondary" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jayegger/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">LinkedIn</a>
        <a class="btn secondary" href="https://github.com/Jcegger" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">GitHub</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
